<h1> Curtin Courses Index </h1>
<p> Welcome to the Curtin Courses Index, a consolidated application for accessing information
about Curtin University courses and units, with data scraped from the Curtin online course handbook. </p>

<p> The primary purpose of this application is to be able to see dependency graphs for units, allowing you to 
choose and plan your prerequisites without manually crawling through the handbook. </p>

